msgid ""
"Rather, the facilitators need to explore the degree of participants "
"experience or knowledge on the subject through Q&A session, after which a "
"discussion follows focusing on difficulties encountered on the subject. The "
"facilitators then can provide additional material that they feel needed by "
"the participants taking into account their prior experience and knowledge."
msgstr ""
"tetapi fasilitator perlu menggali seberapa jauh pengalaman mereka atau "
